-- Turkey's Garanti Bank beats forecasts with 810 mln lira Q2 net profit
-- By Ece Toksabay
-- Thu Jul 24, 2014 10:56AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, July 24 (Reuters) - Turkey's Garanti Bank <GARAN.IS> posted a net profit of 810.4 million lira ($388 million) for the second quarter on Thursday,  above a Reuters poll forecast of 788 million lira.

Second-quarter net profit fell from 887 million lira in the same period a year earlier.